@node Main "DC2Lvl-Expert"

Short:    81 levels for Diamond Caves II
Author:   allan.tnt@post.tele.dk (Allan Rasmussen)
Uploader: allan.tnt@post.tele.dk (Allan Rasmussen)
Type:     game/data
Version:  1.02 (12-Mar-2003)
Url:      http://home19.inet.tele.dk/acme/

These are 81 classic Emerald Mine levels for @{"Diamond Caves II" link DPro},
one player only.

Replay files included.


Difficulty: Hard.


Install: Start the Leveleditor and click on "Import Levels"
(the disk pointing to a drawer) and specify the file Expert.dc2.


Note: Use "Game Options" to turn Audio Off while playing level 72,
or else a bug in Diamondcaves may cause the computer to crash.


Authors: All levels done by Allan Rasmussen,
based upon @{"Expertmine 1" link Emeraldmine} by Leo and Stefan.

@endnode
